ENIAM_LCGparser Version 2.0 :
-----------------------

ENIAM_LCGparser is a library that implements a parser for Logical Categorial Grammar formalism

Install
-------

ENIAM_LCGparser requires OCaml version 4.02.3 compiler
together with Xlib library version 3.2 or later.

In order to install type:

make install

by default, ENIAM_LCGparser is installed in the 'ocamlc -where'/eniam directory.
you can change it by editing the Makefile.

In order to test library type:
make test
./test

test requires pdflatex installed.

